br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20160916/55654821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160916%2F55654821&d=3qbCDYsWA4zLZmsCRWad2AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=72ef9fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160916%2F55654821&h=06600fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20160916/55654821</a><br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌太古城是本港主要藍籌屋苑，早於70年代落成，樓齡最大的第1期，至今已有約38年樓齡。當年太古城最平單位20萬元有找，呎價低於300元。能夠由第一手，持有單位至今近40年的長情業主買少見少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20160916/large/1474026974_faf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160916%2Flarge%2F1474026974_faf6.jpg&h=1790f260&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a77acd1def9755a1eea89c59e397a42ef19845f","tid":765833,"uid":152476,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"係佢地既圈子，錢同樓已經唔係鬥威鬥勁既工具<br />\n而係鬥「白手興家」<br />\n佢地真心覺得自己唔係大食懶二世祖已經係好捱得"},{"pid":"0b508f2e21f19623ed901fedfd29fa5d285e3168","tid":765833,"uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"4f94ddbe0a20c4aebead22711a888799e5626f86","tid":765833,"uid":59848,"like":436,"dislike":3,"score":433,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"當年大學生月薪800 佢借到10萬 即係月薪125倍<br />\n計返宜家大學生月薪中位數15000<br />\n咁計返125倍月薪即係佢借到近190萬創業<br />\n<br />\n成功需父幹 真係好撚勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢借左半層太古城呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係2018年有個23歲既人同你講：「唔畀老竇睇死，借左老豆1000萬創業！」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20160916/55654821\" data-sr-url=\"https:/