":"Wiki 寫佢1948年出世 197x年 拿10萬銀創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   當年10萬買唔買到樓？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"半層太古城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20160916/55654821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160916%2F55654821&d=3qbCDYsWA4zLZmsCRWad2AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=72ef9fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160916%2F55654821&h=06600fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20160916/55654821</a><br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌太古城是本港主要藍籌屋苑，早於70年代落成，樓齡最大的第1期，至今已有約38年樓齡。當年太古城最平單位20萬元有找，呎價低於300元。能夠由第一手，持有單位至今近40年的長情業主買少見少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20160916/large/1474026974_faf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160916%2Flarge%2F1474026974_faf6.jpg&h=1790f260&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"48年出生，23歲即係71年，73年美孚開售都只係110元一呎，十萬可以買到一個大單位，而家一千萬都買唔到<br />\n<br />\n「美孚新邨5期蘭秀道2號高層A室，實用719方呎，1973年發售時的一手價僅8.438萬元」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20140806/18823274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140806%2F18823274&d=3qbCDYsWA4zLZmsCRWad2AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=64191456\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140806%2F18823274&h=39b32077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20140806/18823274</a>"},{"pid":"cd387605911b661119a3e6152904b88c1f0bfc90","tid":765833,"uid":99766,"like":13,"dislike":0